#include<cstdio>
#include<iostream>
#include<string>
using namespace std;
int main() {
//	freopen("inm.txt","r",stdin);
	int n;
	scanf("%d",&n);
	getchar();
	string s,s1;
	cin>>s;
	while(n--) {
		cin >> s1;
		while(1) {
			int p=s.find(s1);
			int q=s1.size();
			if(p==string::npos)
			break;
			s.erase(p,q);
		}
	}
	if(s.size()==0)
	printf("0\n");
	else
	cout<<s<<endl;
	return 0;
}
